# Vault Structure

## Root Level

| Folder | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `team-a/` | Team directory — products, meetings, reference docs |
| `initiatives/` | Time-bound strategic goals |
| `people/` | Person profiles (paired JSON + MD per person) |
| `wraps/` | Hierarchical time-based summaries |
| `Todos.md` | Static task list grouped by owner and priority |

## team-a/ — Product-per-Directory Model

Each product has its own directory with a standard layout:
- `product.md` — entry point describing what we own and current state
- `meetings/` — product-specific meetings
- Additional reference docs co-located with the product

```
team-a/
├── team.md
├── product-x/
│   ├── product.md
│   └── meetings/
├── product-y/
│   ├── product.md
│   └── meetings/
├── reference/
└── meetings/
    ├── 1-on-1-{name}/
    ├── weekly-sync/
    └── adhoc/
```

## Meetings Folders

A `meetings/` subfolder can exist anywhere in the vault. All paths matching `**/meetings/**` are meeting notes.

## wraps/ Hierarchy

```
wraps/
└── YYYY/
    ├── Qx.md
    └── MM/
        ├── month.md
        └── Www/
            ├── week.md
            └── YYYY-MM-DD.md
```

## Naming Conventions

| Pattern | Usage | Location |
|---|---|---|
| `YYYY-MM-DD.md` | Recurring meetings | `**/meetings/` |
| `YYYY-MM-DD - Topic.md` | Dated events | `**/meetings/` |
| `product.md` | Product area entry point | `team-a/{product}/` |
| `Summary.md` | Incremental meeting summary | `**/meetings/{series}/` |
| `Qx.md` | Quarterly wraps | `wraps/YYYY/` |
| `month.md` | Monthly wraps | `wraps/YYYY/MM/` |
| `week.md` | Weekly wraps | `wraps/YYYY/MM/Www/` |
